Changelog
All notable changes to Rythmons will be documented in this file.
The format is based on Keep a Changelog,
and this project adheres to Semantic Versioning.

Unreleased

Added:
Artist profiles with stage name, bio, photo, banner, and image gallery
Venue profiles with address, capacity, type, and image gallery
Media (press/label) profiles linked to artists
Genre tagging for artists and venues (many-to-many)
Geolocation support for artists and venues via French Government Address API (api-adresse.data.gouv.fr)
Radius-based search with Haversine distance filtering for both artists and venues
Full-text search across name, city, bio, genres and owner for artists and venues
Budget range filtering for artists (feeMin/feeMax) and venues (budgetMin/budgetMax)
User role system (ARTIST, ORGANIZER, BOTH) managed via account.updateRole
tRPC API with type-safe end-to-end client/server communication
protectedProcedure middleware for session-based authentication (Better Auth)
prisma-compat.ts for progressive schema migration — optional columns handled gracefully without downtime
Per-user limits: 5 artists, 5 venues, 5 media profiles maximum
Seed script with 3 demo accounts (artist, organizer, both roles)
Turborepo monorepo setup with apps/web, packages/api, packages/db, packages/validation, packages/auth
Deployment pipeline via Vercel with automatic Prisma migration on build (pnpm db:deploy)
